phrases: Y-You sure like to get up close and personal, Alice.
I wanted to share in your good fortune, as well!
You were accepted into the Hero Academy, after all!
You are basically the head of our household now!
I need to talk to you about the Hero Academy.
You see, there is an enrollment fee...
I have some money saved up.
I will earn the money myself.
Three hundred thousand rels to get into the school, eh?
That is probably a bit harsh for a poor noble like you.
I do not think you needed to be that blunt about it, but yeah.
Then why do not you fight some rare monsters in this dungeon and sell them off?
I would rather not bring that much attention to myself.
Could you just say it was you who defeated the Dead Reaper?
People would have an easier time believing the daughter of an earl defeated it
than the son of a baronet.
I will say that I defeated it.
I ended up letting my vain classmate take the credit for it.
Then I guess there is only one way.
Sir, please do not intimidate the newbie.
Is this your first time at the adventurers' guild?
First, allow me to explain the very simple system we use here.
There are many prominent adventurers who belong to Odin.
cull monsters, explore dungeons, and complete various other quests.
Adventurers have ranks, which affect the quests they can take
Of course, those who show consistent results may rank up.
In order to join the guild, we will need you to register.
First, I will need you to write down all the skills you currently have.
All that information will be classified with the guild.
I would appreciate it if you did not kid around.
We do not have an endless supply of paper.
I am sure Get Creative and Editor probably sound pretty weird.
No, I am aware of those skills.
This is Odin, the guild that Olivia Servant was a member of.
I let the cat out of the bag.
We do get people like you every now and then...
People who claim to be Olivia's successor.
Let us find out the truth.
When you touch this Discerning Tome, your skills appear in writing.
You still have a chance to take back what you said.
I will go ahead and do this.
But what happens if I am not lying?
How about I lift up my skirt and say, I am terribly sorry, Lord Noir.
Noir Stardia 16 years old Level 33 Skills: Great Sage Get Creative Editor Bestow LP Conversion Stone Bullet Discerning Eye
So, what were you going to do again?
Were not you supposed to say, Lord Noir, I love you?
So, what kind of quest would you like?
You will have to start at Rank E.
Actually, I need to get 300,000 rels in a week.
but they are super rare bugs that are seldom seen, right?
but we started taking E-Rank applicants, as well.
So I am guessing you could not find anyone to take the quest...
But, Noir, you have a useful skill
I have very high hopes for you.
I find capable men very attractive.
I-It is hard to believe she doubted me a few moments ago...
The grasshoppers' habitat should be around here.
If I use the Great Sage skill that answers any question,
I should be able to find them quickly.
But kisses are absolutely necessary to avoid the headache side effect.
If I use Get Creative to make Headache Immunity...
But I cannot always rely on Emma...
Great Sage, where are the rainbow grasshoppers?
The closest one to this location is 310 meters to the south, behind a boulder.
It would be nice to just have Emma here with me...
H-How did you find out about that?
I went to your house, and they said you went to the guild.
Then I went to the guild, and...
Actually, the details do not matter!
How could you do this without talking to me first?
I thought it might be too dangerous for you.
Do not you remember our promise from six years ago?
and I yelled, We will be together forever, until death do us part?
So I will look for these grasshoppers with you!
You will be using Great Sage, right?
Oh, you do not have to kiss me anymore.
B-But, I mean, it is basically a greeting, so you can give me one anytime.
And we have been friends forever.
And even with the immunity, I still get a slight headache...
Though, honestly, this headache is quite manageable.
At this rate, you will rank up in no time.
So you are capable and hardworking.
You truly are a fine gentleman.
And because you are such a fine gentleman, I have another quest for you.
It is a quest to take care of some monsters.
Feel free to ask me any questions you might have.
I am going to become an adventurer so I can come with you on this quest, Noir.
Noir and I have been friends since we were kids.
The Hidden Dungeon Only I Can Enter.
I am in charge of Noir.
I would appreciate it if you would not interfere.
We are together forever, until death do us part.
Are they having a lovers' spat?
W-Well, this turned into a spectacle...
I am so blessed to have you help me out!
And Lola, I will do whatever it takes to give you the best results I can!
I guess that is enough for today.
On behalf of Mr. Noir's looks.
Let us have dinner off the clock sometime.
You seriously had the nerve to do that right in front of me?!
Do not you know girls can be conniving?
Go to dinner with her, and she will drag you into a room and...
Hey, there is a patch of grass missing.
I wonder if it is because the Big Rabbit that we are after ate some.
Apparently those rabbits are disrupting the ecosystem.
We will get 50,000 rels if we get rid of them.
I will take the one on the right!
Then I will use Stone Bullet!
As a fellow guy, I feel for you, but...
Okay, now to back up Emma.
I will defeat that thing myself.
If you do all the work, that girl's going to be all over you again!
It is so fast for its size!
She is like a butterfly dancing on the wind.
All right, let us do this!
It will probably come looking for us soon.
We need to figure out how to deal with that thing.
Why could not I defeat it?
Maybe its skin was too thick and you just could not reach its vital point.
She is actually depressed about this.
There must be something I can do.
Okay, if I use Get Creative
Needed to Get Creative LP. 300 Bestow to Emma LP. 400 Total Used LP. 700
and Bestow the stronger Dual-Wielded Daggers (Grade B) to her...
Improves wielder's handling of dual-wielded daggers
Then maybe I can use Editor and tweak her skill itself...
Significantly improves wielder's handling of dual-wielded daggers
If I use 500 right now, I might be in trouble.
Yeah, but there is something that I need in return.
I-If It will help me defeat the rabbit, I will do anything!
Can I nibble on your ear?
I-I promise I will not bite hard...
Do whatever you want with me.
I did not know ears were so soft.
but I guess there is still a lot I do not know about her.
Now to use Editor to change Emma's skill!
I have actually seen them plenty of times.
You can keep looking at them, just for today.
It is to thank you... for making me stronger!
Th-This is truly... proof that you completed your quest.
Did you really do this on your own?
Emma took down the Big Rabbit all on her own!
I gained some confidence because of this quest.
I apologize for my prior rudeness.
I heard that Big Rabbit flesh is delicious.
It is hard to come by.
I hear adventurers eat the meat right after they defeat them.
Well, you see, I happened to created a skill called Pocket Dimension
that allows me to store large items in another dimension.
Let us all have some together.
You are amazing at your job and considerate...
Barbecue Is a Battlefield, by Emma Brightness.
Noir, here is your reward for this quest.
Looks like you have enough for your enrollment fee now.
Congratulations on getting accepted to the school.
Cheers to the adventurers of Odin!
Just call us if you need any help.
You should join my party next time!
Who do I thank for this?
Noir, everyone is waiting to hear you speak!
It is all thanks to you, Master!
I will come see you again...
You could come see me right now!
